r />\n<br />\n<br />\n間桐櫻啱小弟口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be4fcca09834b66e140011d4e2fdf7089119650","tid":1097310,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:19:19.000Z","msg":"雷姆係綾波系既進化形<br />\n<br />\n有母性既包容力 冇臭西格 但又唔係無口  有互動<br />\n為左主角去死都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1651e20e049be131d3c7a7f51eed0e4d15b0a1ed","tid":1097310,"uid":154127,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2adaf8e1c409c5de9475f0659f28b49a43ab5623","tid":1097310,"uid":198822,"like":30,"dislike":4,"score":26,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:17:10.000Z","msg":"間桐櫻<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.snupps.com/api/2.10/users/1493111/items/14940628/views/15988352-1.1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.snupps.com%2Fapi%2F2.10%2Fusers%2F1493111%2Fitems%2F14940628%2Fviews%2F15988352-1.1024.jpg&h=fce50c39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n櫻被強姦/改造身體呢啲不幸遭遇有咩好笑<br />\n唔知樓上啲偏激毒撚份人係真係咁戇鳩呀定點<br />\n我就睇唔透<br />\n夠膽咪係現實對住個強姦受害者笑鳩人囉 諒你地又唔敢<br />\n<br />\n身逢不幸而不甘就此凋亡<br />\n背負聖杯咒詛之物 自憐不如家姐<br />\n但佢忍咗落嚟<br />\n捱過十數年來蟲老嘅折磨 頂住被阿哥折辱嘅羞恥<br />\n直到小安附身 依然心心念念士郎嘅性命<br />\n去到最後 即使殺害無數平民 重創親生家姐 <br />\n依然無被罪惡感壓垮 壓制住攻擊士郎嘅黑泥化身<br />\n<br />\n因為聖杯戰爭之中數夜縈迴停駐嘅情意 因為衛宮士郎畀佢嘅勇氣<br />\n櫻終於獲得救贖  <br />\n春日漫天嘅花瓣  最後可以為相依嘅有情人而飛舞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n間桐櫻啱小弟口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:19:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />志同道合"},{"pid":"d5fd9f37a5441005f9584e994011183a5edb8143","tid":1097310,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:26:17.000Z","msg":"櫻性格好完美<br />\n但我鍾意凜多啲"},{"pid":"53cb58192df1fb5bd8a1ab3e573f1fb782098e4c","tid":1097310,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"BOTH!!!"},{"pid":"d9d75aad7ca06297cd6027853dae2c4adbacbc27